sequenceDiagram
    actor Player
    participant Browser as Browser<br/>(index.html/scoreboard.js)
    participant GameUI as game render.js<br/>(/plugins/{gameId}/render.js)
    participant Hub as GameHub (SignalR)
    participant Api as Api Endpoints
    participant Disp as IDispatcher
    participant Mgr as GameSessionManager
    participant Game as IGame (X01Game, in ALC)
    participant Db as SQLite (ThrowRecord)
    participant Det as Detection source<br/>(Manual REST / Mock / AutoDarts)

    Player->>Browser: GET /api/games, pick X01 + input source
    Browser->>Api: POST /api/matches
    Api->>Db: persist Match (InputSource, BoardId binding)
    Api-->>Browser: matchId, gameId
    Browser->>Browser: full page load with matchId/gameId
    Browser->>GameUI: fetch /plugins/{gameId}/render.js<br/>(404 -> default fallback renderer)
    Browser->>Hub: JoinMatch(matchId)

    loop each dart / turn / undo
        Player->>Det: throw a dart (click dartboard.js OR real board / mock stream)
        Det->>Api: POST manual-throw / manual-end-turn / undo<br/>(or DetectionListenerService await-foreach)
        Api->>Disp: Send(RecordDetectedThrowCommand / EndOfTurn / UndoLastThrow)
        Disp->>Mgr: resolve IGame for matchId (per-matchId lock)
        Mgr->>Game: ReceiveThrow / ReceiveEvent / UndoLastThrow
        alt illegal input
            Game-->>Disp: throws GameRuleViolationException
            Disp-->>Api: ErrorOr failure
            Api-->>Det: 4xx response
        else valid
            Game-->>Disp: state mutated (async, in-process ALC)
            Disp->>Db: persist/retract ThrowRecord
            Disp->>Game: GetState()
            Game-->>Disp: GameStateSnapshot (incl. Payload)
            Disp->>Disp: Publish(GameStateChangedEvent)
            Disp->>Hub: GameHubNotifier.SendAsync("GameStateUpdated", snapshot)
            Hub-->>Browser: push GameStateUpdated(snapshot)
            Browser->>Browser: update shared chrome<br/>(players, scores, leg/set, history)
            Browser->>GameUI: window.renderGameBoard(container, snapshot)
            GameUI-->>Browser: game-specific board region updated
        end
    end

    Game-->>Disp: IsComplete == true, GetResult()
    Disp->>Hub: final GameStateUpdated (winner)
    Hub-->>Browser: push
    Browser->>Player: winner banner shown
